Package src.swimmingpoolproblem.swimmingpool

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Basket
    The Basket class describes a basket containing clothes.
    BasketPool
    BasketPool describes a pool of baskets which can be provided to swimmers.
    Cubicle
    The Cubicle class describes a cubicle where people can get dressed or get undressed.
    CubiclePool
    CubiclePool describes a pool providing cubicles to swimmers.
    DressAction
    DressAction describes an action where a swimmer get dressed in a specified amount of steps.
    SwimAction
    SwimAction describes an action where a swimmer swims in a specified number of steps.
    Swimmer
    The Swimmer class describes a Swimmer at the swimming pool executing several actions in a sequential order.
    UndressAction
    DressAction describes an action where a swimmer get undressed in a specified amount of steps.
